name: Psychiatrist
description: Medical doctor who specializes in mental health

name: Oncologist
description: Medical professional who specializes in the diagnosis and treatment of cancer

name: Orthopedic
description: Medical professional who focuses on treating the musculoskeletal system

name: Ophthalmologist
description: Medical doctor who specializes in eye and vision care

name: Endocrinologist
description: Medical doctor who specializes in the diagnosis and treatment of hormone-related health conditions

name: Gastroenterologist
description: Medical specialist who focuses on the health of the digestive system and the liver

name: Pediatrician
description: Medical doctor who specializes in providing care for children from birth through childhood

name: Dermatologist
description: Medical doctor who specializes in diagnosing and treating conditions that affect the skin

name: Neurologist
description: Medical doctor who specializes in identifying and treating diseases of the nervous system

name: Cardiologist
description: Medical doctor who specializes in the study or treatment of heart diseases and heart abnormalities
